Polish August Wage Growth Reaches 5.4%, Tops Median Forecast

-- B y   M a r t a   W a l d o c h
-- 
2011-09-16T12:01:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/polish-august-wage-growth-reaches-5-4-tops-median-forecast.html
Polish corporate wages rose 5.4
percent on the year in August, the  Central Statistical Office 
reported in Warsaw today. The figure was above the median
forecast of 4.9 percent in a Bloomberg survey of 22 economists.  Employment increased 3.1 percent in August from a year
earlier, compared with the 3.3 percent median forecast by 21
economists in a Bloomberg survey.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marta Waldoch in Warsaw at 
 mwaldoch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
